  "history": "The client has experienced chronic depression and isolation since late adolescence, with ongoing difficulties forming and maintaining friendships. A recent breakup preceded a depressive relapse, and the client has a history of using SSRIs, with recent medication adjustments. The pattern of isolation and negative self-evaluation appears longstanding, and the breakup likely intensified feelings of rejection and hopelessness.",
